Information
------------------------------

Nick Baker's Wild West
Presenter Nick Baker looks at the diverse and wonderful wildlife to be found around the south west of England.


1)  Coast 
Wildlife documentary series where Nick Baker explores the south west of England. In the first episode, Nick discovers the natural wonders living around the stunning coastal areas of the region.

2)  River Valleys 
Naturalist Nick Baker explores the steep-sided river valleys of Devon and Cornwall on his journey through the stunning landscape of south west England.

3)  Wetlands 
Naturalist Nick Baker explores the wildlife-rich wetlands of south west England, including two stunning Somerset reserves.
